    "description": "G4SNVHunter is an R/Bioconductor package designed to identify genomic sequences with G4-forming propensity and to screen single nucleotide variants (SNVs) for their potential to destabilize G4 structures. It leverages the G4Hunter algorithm and is used to investigate how genetic variants might influence biological functions by impacting G4 formation.",
